edu.birzeit.swen6301.model

Class Manifest

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.birzeit.swen6301.model.Manifest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPart

    public class Manifest
extends java.lang.Object
implements IPart
    To encapsulate and organize all related specifications (segments & links) of certain manifest file contents.

    Main Functions:

    1. Call mirror's stream to download manifest contents by using from URL.

    2. Split segments as text array from whole manifest text that has been fetched from that URL.

    3. Bind segment objects into attached list.
